  <h2>
    <span class="">以下豆列推荐</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1418776/doulists">全部</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/113608/" target="_blank">刘新老师的书单（国际政治、社会政治、哲学、心理学、方法论等）</a>
                <span class="pl">(孤独心俱乐部)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/1268584/" target="_blank">王沪宁</a>
